the different department heads to prepare and submit their individual Project Procurement Management Plan (PPMP) to the BAC for consolidation. The BAC through the BAC Secretariat shall prepare the APP to guide in the procurement of goods and shall be meticulously and judiciously followed in the procurement process to minimize the procurement of goods through SVP;
the BAC evaluate the frequency of SVP as an alternative mode of procurement being resorted to and ensure that the conditions for SVP as an alternative mode of procurement have been satisfied;
the BAC practice the conduct of public bidding in the procurement process in order to ensure the most advantageous price and avail of discounts and generate income from sale of bid documents;
the BAC through its Secretariat accomplish and fill-up the data especially the dates in the RFQs and Abstract of Quotation and comply with the necessary requirements for completeness and propriety of the transactions; and
the Municipal Accountant check, verify and ensure the completeness of the supporting documents before processing the claims to avoid suspension in Audit.
